      "content": "the drooping isn't that bad, i just noticed it in the mirror but it's probably just because of the swelling from the headache. i don't have a fever or anything so i don't think it's an infection. if it is a migraine, what's the best way to get rid of it quickly? i have some extra strong migraine meds and some other stuff in my cabinet, can i just mix them to make it work faster?",
